    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/5b5b35499e2c6d2697eb0b7684af4a9e.poster.avif?t=1727716569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/5b5b35499e2c6d2697eb0b7684af4a9e.webm?t=1727716569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/5b5b35499e2c6d2697eb0b7684af4a9e.mp4?t=1727716569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>紧盯弹幕炼狱的深处，然后将投来之物悉数奉还！《Deflector》是一款张力十足的roguelite游戏，你可以使用能力将敌人的投射物反弹回去。配合独特的武器和突变，以你自己的方式消除致命的病毒。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/aea5eeec5ac453f6d7ef66c23a87c12f.avif?t=1727716569\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>每种生物壳都拥有独特的武器、技能和偏转投射物的方式，从中选择你喜欢的生物壳。刚开始，可选生物壳为投掷回旋镖的根除者，随后玩家可以在实验中不断体验生死轮回，以此解锁更多生物壳。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/2c91e9d5a4b4569afcd69178d7d96d0a.poster.avif?t=1727716569\" width=620 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/2c91e9d5a4b4569afcd69178d7d96d0a.webm?t=1727716569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/2c91e9d5a4b4569afcd69178d7d96d0a.mp4?t=1727716569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/eaa2f758e91cbbce4520fede30b46ead.avif?t=1727716569\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>你的中心拥有各种协助病毒研究的模块。通过战斗积累经验，解锁更多的突变、生物壳和持续的升级。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/606b88c2c0b46f317dcd3ec6f5e61820.poster.avif?t=1727716569\" width=620 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/606b88c2c0b46f317dcd3ec6f5e61820.webm?t=1727716569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/606b88c2c0b46f317dcd3ec6f5e61820.mp4?t=1727716569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/0cf4d7a0786648a4449b76bf12353023.avif?t=1727716569\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>每个世界都充斥着独一无二的敌对生物，它们随时准备用尸体和弹幕将你淹没其中。从最弱小的生物到每个世界尽头的终极病毒，每种威胁都相当致命。吸取试验和致命错误带来的经验，全力战胜每一个敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/c3600d5e24dc596e956147a789cd2419.poster.avif?t=1727716569\" width=620 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/c3600d5e24dc596e956147a789cd2419.webm?t=1727716569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736550/extras/c3600d5e24dc596e956147a789cd2419.mp4?t=1727716569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
